<p> Marie Christine Petiquay is a young attikamekw who grew up in Manawan. She will be graduating in social Sciences and Humanities at the Kiuna Institution in Odanak this summer.
  Leaving her community to pursue her education in a non-indigenous college was really hard hence she had to come back to Manawan.
  More than a dedicated student Marie-Christine is also an artist in various ways, curious to foster her creative abilities and experiment.</p>
